name: Cherry Dana’s life before plastic surgery | The Adults Corner
summary: Welcome to Episode 1 of The Adults Corner Podcast with Cherry Dana and Chloe Pillans.   Our first episode is all about Cherry, as she let’s us into her world before plastic surgery, before the fame, before the success, and all the way up until now.   Topics covered in this episode are:  “Nothing goes in my butt!” Cherry gets attacked in her hometown. Life before plastic surgery. Ex-Con friends in Mexico.
